title: One dead, 8 injured in Grand Rapids shooting
content:
GRAND RAPIDS, Mich. (WILX) - One person is dead and eight others are injured after a shooting in Grand Rapids early Sunday morning.
It happened around 4:00 a.m. at a strip mall.
Police say about 60 people were gathered for a party there when the shooting started.
Officers say a man in his early twenties was killed. He was pronounced dead at the scene.
Police have released no details about the suspect.
